title: 273. Did China Eat America’s Jobs?
description: For years, economists promised that global free trade would be mostly win-win. Now they admit the pace of change has been "traumatic." This has already led to a political insurrection -- so what's next?
author: editor@freakonomics.com (Freakonomics Radio + Stitcher)
